Umdaniso webhaleyi Ibhaleyi luhlobo lomdaniso owaqalwa kwiinkundla zeItalian Renaissance ngenkulungwane ye-15, nolwathi lwaphuhliswa ngakumbi eFrance naseRussia njengohlobo lomdaniso wekonisathi. Iziqendu zayo zokuqala zandulela ukuyilwa kweqonga le-proscenium kwaye zathi zaboniswa kwiindawo ezinkulu apho uninzi lwababukeli luhleli phantsi kumanqwanqwa okanye amaqonga kuwo omathathu amacala omgangatho wokudanisa. Iye ke ukusukela ngoko yaba lolona hlobo lomdaniso onegama lawo. Ubukhulu becala wenziwa ukhatshwa ngumculo weklasiki kwaye lo mdaniso unempembelelo enkulu njengohlobo lomdaniso wehlabathi. Ibhola yombhoxo IBHOLA YOMBHOXO EMZANTSI AFRIKA[tshintsha | edit source] ngumdlalo othandwa kakhulu ngabantu, odlalwa kakhulu eMzantsi Afrika. Lena ibhola ixatyiswe kakhulu eMzantsi Africa. Iqela ispring bok liqukunjelwa nje ngeqela eliphakathi kwamaqela amakhulu elizweni elathi lathatha indebe ezimbini emazweni jikelele iRugby world cup. Ekufikeni kukaCanon George Ogilive kwiDiocesan College eKapa ngo1861, ufike wayintloko-mpathi wazisa ibhola yombhoxo edlalwa nase Winchester College. IBhola yombhoxo iqale kwiphupha lokudlalisa umnyazi kwizikolo zokufundisa umbhoxo, kwaye ibiliphupha lokuqala lokudlalisa umnyazi kwizikolo iEnglish public schools kwiminyka edlulileyo.

KuYohane 8:44, uYesu wathi uMtyholi ‘ akazange eme enyanisweni,’ nto leyo ethetha ukuba wakha wangumntu onenyani. Noko ke, njengazo zonke izidalwa zikaThixo, le ngelosi eyaba nguSathana yayinenkululeko yokuzikhethela ukwenza okubi okanye okulungileyo. Xa wakhetha ukuma nxamnye noThixo waza waphembelela isibini sokuqala ukuba simlandele, wajika waba nguSathana, igama elithetha “Umchasi.”—Genesis 3:1-5; ISityhilelo 12:9.

Imithetho elishumi Imithetho elishumi ikwaziwa ngokuba yiDecalogue yingqokolela yemithetho nemigaqo emakuhanjwe ngayo ngokwebhayibhile. Le mithethi imalunga nendlela abantu amaziphathe ngayo nangndlela emasMnqule ngayo uMdali wethu. Le mithetho ixatyiswe kakhulu kwinkolo yamaJuda neyamaKrestu. Iquka imithetho ethi MNYE kuphela Ofanelwe kukunqulwa, nguThixo, kugcinwe umhla weSabatha, kutshatyalaliswe izithixo, ubugqi, ubugebenga, ubusela, ubuxoki, nokukrexeza. Amaqela ngokwahlukana kwawo aneenkolelo zawo ezahlukileyo kule mithetho, ngokwendlela etolikwa nelandelelana ngayo ngokweendlela enonjolwe ngayo le mithetho.

Uza kufunda indlela ubomi nokufa kukaYesu okunokukunceda ngayo. Funda Okungakumbi Ziyintoni Iindaba Ezilungileyo? Funda ngesizathu sokuba uYesu eze emhlabeni nokuba thina singenelwa njani namhlanje.

Mpuma Koloni IMpuma Koloni liphondo eliseMzantsi Afrika kodwa ikomkhulu lalo liseBhisho naseMonti. Lasekwa ngo-1994 kumaphandle ayezimele asemaXhoseni, iTranskei and Ciskei, kunye nenxalenye esempuma kwiPhondo leKoloni. Yindawo le ekwafikela kuyo abelungu ababesuka phesheya abafika ngo-1820. Umbindi kunye nempuma yeli phondo likhaya kuhlanga lwamaXhosa. Lo mmandla yindawo ekuzalelwe kuyo amaqhawe aziwayo ezopolitiko oMzantsi Afrika afana noNelson Mandela, Oliver Tambo, Walter Sisulu, Govan Mbeki, Raymond Mhlaba, Chris Hani, Thabo Mbeki, Steve Biko noCharles Coghlan.
